lyrics:
[verse]
Baby, you had my heart, but you tore it apart
I thought we were forever, but it was just a false start
Now I'm drowning in these tears, but I'll find a brand new spark
Gotta let go of the pain, it's time to make a fresh start

[chorus]
Heartbreak ain't gonna break me, I'm moving on
Now I'm better off without you, I don't need your love
I'm getting on my shit, putting myself above
No more tears in my eyes, it's time to rise above
